{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/firebase/using-firebaseui/","webpackCompilationHash":"0478f4b3e93cd5fcb2ef","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"692a13c7-f1c9-54bd-9b1e-8429a509eec2","html":"<blockquote>\n<p>이 포스트에서는 firebaseui를 이용한 로그인 환경 구축을 목표로 한다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/firebase/firebaseui-web\"><strong>firebaseui-web</strong></a> 관련 문서를 기반으로 한다.</p>\n<h1 id=\"firebase-\"><a href=\"#firebase-\" aria-label=\"firebase  permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>firebase ?</h1>\n<p>파이어베이스(firebase)는 구글에서 제공하고 있는 모바일 및 웹 애플리케이션 개발 플랫폼이다. </p>\n<p>웹에서 사용할 DB를 저장해 줄 수 있으며, 사진과 같은 자료를 storage에 저장 가능하다. 또한 로그인 계정을 Authentication에서 관리 가능하며, google, facebook, github와 같은 다양한 플랫폼과 로그인 계정을 연동하여 사용이 가능하다.</p>\n<p>웹 서비스의 호스팅을 firebase를 통해 할 수 있으며, <del>유료 버전이긴 하지만</del> ML Kit 이름의 머신러닝 kit도 제공하고 있다.</p>\n<p>DB는 json 형식으로 제공하며, 상당히 편한 방식으로 현재 사용자에 대한 정보를 알아 낼 수 있어 사용에 용이하다. </p>\n<p>단점으로는, firebase가 제공하는것이 다양하나, 개발자의 custom이 어렵다. authentication에서 제공하는 범위를 넘어가는 정보를 user에게 포함시키고 싶다면 따로 user db를 생성해서 user를 관리하는 방식으로 관리를 해야만 한다.</p>\n<h1 id=\"firebaseui-web-\"><a href=\"#firebaseui-web-\" aria-label=\"firebaseui web  permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>firebaseui-web ?</h1>\n<p>firebaseui-web은 firebase와 다른 플랫폼간의 로그인 및 회원가입을 용이하게 해준다. ui가 예쁘게 제공되어 있어 사용하기만 하면 쉽게 사용이 가능하다.</p>\n<p>로그인 페이지를 구현하기 이전에, 기본 사용할 페이지는 vue를 사용한다. 만약 vue 페이지가 없다면 <a href=\"https://sweetlog.netlify.com/Vue/using-vue-with-vuex-vue-router-vuetify/\">Vue router, Vuex, vuetify 사용하기</a> 를 참고하여 페이지를 구현한다. (vuetify는 사용하지 않는다.)</p>\n<h2 id=\"firebase-콘솔-생성\"><a href=\"#firebase-%EC%BD%98%EC%86%94-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"firebase 콘솔 생성 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>firebase 콘솔 생성</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://console.firebase.google.com/\">firebase console</a> 사이트에 접속. 새로운 프로젝트를 생성하는것이 가장 먼저 해야하는 일이다.</p>\n<p>프로젝트 추가 버튼을 누르고 나오는 작성란을 다음과 같이 채운다.</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/96b42da1c852aebc54c53369b0a43189/a83d3/firebaseconsole.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 960px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 70.00828500414251%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"firebaseconsole\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/96b42da1c852aebc54c53369b0a43189/f570d/firebaseconsole.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/96b42da1c852aebc54c53369b0a43189/0783d/firebaseconsole.png 240w,\n/static/96b42da1c852aebc54c53369b0a43189/782f4/firebaseconsole.png 480w,\n/static/96b42da1c852aebc54c53369b0a43189/f570d/firebaseconsole.png 960w,\n/static/96b42da1c852aebc54c53369b0a43189/a83d3/firebaseconsole.png 1207w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/123f5d3cc3e6ec7982781046b9eaf483/a6906/firebase-loading.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 728px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 92.03296703296704%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"firebase-loading\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/123f5d3cc3e6ec7982781046b9eaf483/a6906/firebase-loading.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/123f5d3cc3e6ec7982781046b9eaf483/0783d/firebase-loading.png 240w,\n/static/123f5d3cc3e6ec7982781046b9eaf483/782f4/firebase-loading.png 480w,\n/static/123f5d3cc3e6ec7982781046b9eaf483/a6906/firebase-loading.png 728w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 728px) 100vw, 728px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>로딩이 끝나면 시작하기를 눌러 새롭게 시작하면 된다.</p>\n<p>좌측 개발 탭에서 Authentication 탭을 선택하면 아직 사용자가 로그인 한 적이 없기 때문에 다음과 같이 사용자가 존재하지 않는다.</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/777b7611147df6869432cb99cd903d46/fbfd0/firebase-authentication.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 960px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 61.28048780487805%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"firebase-authentication\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/777b7611147df6869432cb99cd903d46/f570d/firebase-authentication.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/777b7611147df6869432cb99cd903d46/0783d/firebase-authentication.png 240w,\n/static/777b7611147df6869432cb99cd903d46/782f4/firebase-authentication.png 480w,\n/static/777b7611147df6869432cb99cd903d46/f570d/firebase-authentication.png 960w,\n/static/777b7611147df6869432cb99cd903d46/fbfd0/firebase-authentication.png 1312w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>위 사진에서 빨간색으로 밑줄친 로그인 방법에 들어간 후 이메일/비밀번호를 클릭한다.</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e04f543892c6cb8910b85f96bbde502c/14c50/firebase-authentication-eamil1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 960px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 45.69420035149385%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"firebase-authentication-eamil1\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/e04f543892c6cb8910b85f96bbde502c/f570d/firebase-authentication-eamil1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e04f543892c6cb8910b85f96bbde502c/0783d/firebase-authentication-eamil1.png 240w,\n/static/e04f543892c6cb8910b85f96bbde502c/782f4/firebase-authentication-eamil1.png 480w,\n/static/e04f543892c6cb8910b85f96bbde502c/f570d/firebase-authentication-eamil1.png 960w,\n/static/e04f543892c6cb8910b85f96bbde502c/14c50/firebase-authentication-eamil1.png 1138w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>위와 같이 사용설정을 한 후 저장한다. 그렇게 되면 상태가 사용 설정됨으로 변경된다. 이렇게 되면 기본적으로 이메일/비밀번호로 로그인이 가능하게 된다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"login-router-생성\"><a href=\"#login-router-%EC%83%9D%EC%84%B1\" aria-label=\"login router 생성 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>login router 생성</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>로그인을 할 view 페이지인 <code class=\"language-text\">Loginl.vue</code> 파일을 <code class=\"language-text\">views</code>폴더 아래에 생성한다.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">src/views/Login.vue</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vue\"><pre class=\"language-vue\"><code class=\"language-vue\">&lt;template&gt;\n &lt;v-container&gt;\n   &lt;h1&gt;Login&lt;/h1&gt;\n &lt;/v-container&gt;\n&lt;/template&gt;\n\n&lt;script&gt;\nexport default {\n\n}\n&lt;/script&gt;\n\n&lt;style&gt;\n\n&lt;/style&gt;</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>주소 설정을 위해 <code class=\"language-text\">router.js</code>에 Login 주소를 추가한다.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">src/router.js</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> Home <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'./views/Home.vue'</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> Login <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'./views/Login.vue'</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\nroutes<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n   <span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\n   <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n     path<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'/login'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n     name<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'login'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n     component<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> Login\n   <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>로그인을 위한 Login을 import 하여 component로 사용한다.</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6a2f63f8d7bbcd191d0a06677f3e1386/13a77/vue-router-login.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 844px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 47.274881516587676%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"vue-router-login\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/6a2f63f8d7bbcd191d0a06677f3e1386/13a77/vue-router-login.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6a2f63f8d7bbcd191d0a06677f3e1386/0783d/vue-router-login.png 240w,\n/static/6a2f63f8d7bbcd191d0a06677f3e1386/782f4/vue-router-login.png 480w,\n/static/6a2f63f8d7bbcd191d0a06677f3e1386/13a77/vue-router-login.png 844w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 844px) 100vw, 844px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>이렇게 지정을 해주게 되면 /login 페이지로 접속했을 경우 login 페이지가 열리게 된다.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"firebaseui-기본-사용-설정\"><a href=\"#firebaseui-%EA%B8%B0%EB%B3%B8-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9-%EC%84%A4%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"firebaseui 기본 사용 설정 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>firebaseui 기본 사용 설정</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>firebase와 firebaseui를 npm으로 설치한다.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>firebaseui를 사용하기 위해서는 cdn으로 불러오거나, npm으로 설치하는 방법이 존재한다. CDN으로 불러와서 구현하는 것은 다른 페이지에서 많이 보이고 있으나, vue에서 npm 설치하는 자료가 부족한 것 같아 이 포스트에서는 npm 설치로 진행한다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> firebase --save\n$ <span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> firebaseui --save</code></pre></div>\n<p>사용하고 있는 터미널에 두 명령어를 사용하여 firebase와 firebaseui를 설치한다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>firebaseui가 제공하고 있는 js와 css 파일을 import 한다.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">main.js</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> store <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'./store'</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// firebaseui css</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'../node_modules/firebaseui/dist/firebaseui.js'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'../node_modules/firebaseui/dist/firebaseui.css'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>들어가야 하는 위치는 크게 중요하지 않으나 들어가야 하는 파일은 중요하다.</p>\n<p>Vue router에서는 css 및 js의 import 위치를 router로 받아 url로 접속시켜버린다. 때문에 <code class=\"language-text\">index.html</code>의 head 안에 넣는다면 제대로 import 되지 않는다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>위에서 만든 <code class=\"language-text\">login.vue</code>에 우리가 사용할 firebase의 기본 설정을 해줘야한다.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">views/Login.vue</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>script<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> firebaseui <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'firebaseui'</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> firebase <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"firebase/app\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> config <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n apiKey<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"&lt;api-key>\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n authDomain<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"&lt;project-id>.firebaseapp.com\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n databaseURL<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"https://&lt;project-id>.firebaseio.com\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n projectId<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"&lt;project-id>\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nfirebase<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">initializeApp</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>config<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> auth <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> firebase<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">auth</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> ui <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">firebaseui<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>auth<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>AuthUI</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>auth<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>script<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>firebase에 접근해서 사용하기 위해서는 firebase에서 제공한 apiKey와 도메인, db url등과 같은 다양한 정보를 입력해야한다.</p>\n<p>다양한 정보를 넘겨 요청을 보낼 수 있지만 여기에서는 config 에 선언된 정보들만 보낼것이다. &#x3C;> 표시 안에 있는 내용들을 채우면 되고, 이 내용은 firebase의 설정에서 찾을 수 있다.</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/35e18c23158548e0d7996e864b8481c0/1bb9b/firebase-setting.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 960px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 63.61957525392429%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"firebase-setting\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/35e18c23158548e0d7996e864b8481c0/f570d/firebase-setting.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/35e18c23158548e0d7996e864b8481c0/0783d/firebase-setting.png 240w,\n/static/35e18c23158548e0d7996e864b8481c0/782f4/firebase-setting.png 480w,\n/static/35e18c23158548e0d7996e864b8481c0/f570d/firebase-setting.png 960w,\n/static/35e18c23158548e0d7996e864b8481c0/1bb9b/firebase-setting.png 1083w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>좌측 상단의 톱니바퀴를 누른 후 프로젝트 설정에 들어가면 다음과 같은 페이지가 나온다. 여기의 프로젝트 ID와 웹 API키를 위의 코드에 잘 넣어준다.</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"email-로그인\"><a href=\"#email-%EB%A1%9C%EA%B7%B8%EC%9D%B8\" aria-label=\"email 로그인 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>email 로그인</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Login.vue</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"vue\"><pre class=\"language-vue\"><code class=\"language-vue\">&lt;template&gt;\n  &lt;v-container&gt;\n    &lt;h1&gt;Login&lt;/h1&gt;\n    &lt;div id=&quot;firebaseui-auth-container&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n  &lt;/v-container&gt;\n&lt;/template&gt;\n\n&lt;script&gt;\n...\n\nexport default {\n  methods: {\n    initUI: function() {\n      // template에 존재하는 div에 ui.start 명령어를 사용하면 firebaseui가 알아서 그려준다.\n      ui.start(&quot;#firebaseui-auth-container&quot;, {\n        // 현재 사용하는 옵션은 이메일 로그인만 사용한다.\n        signInoptions: [firebase.auth.EmailAuthProvider.PROVIDER_ID],\n        callbacks: {\n          // 로그인이 성공하면,\n          signInSuccessWithAuthResult: (authResult, redirectUrl) =&gt; {\n            // 로그인 정보를 각각의 data에 저장한다.\n            alert(`${authResult.user.displayName}login 성공!`);\n            return false;\n          }\n        }\n      });\n      \n    }\n    \n  },\n  mounted: function() {\n    // 현재 로그인한 회원의 정보를 알 수 있는 함수이다. 존재하면 딕셔너리가, 아니면 null값이 나온다.\n    auth.onAuthStateChanged((user) =&gt;{\n        if (user) {\n          alert(&quot;이미 로그인 한 사용자입니다!&quot;);\n        }\n        //현재 유저가 존재하지 않으면 로그인창을 보여준다.\n        this.initUI()\n    })\n  }\n}\n&lt;/script&gt;</code></pre></div>\n<p>로그인 아래에 id가 <code class=\"language-text\">firebaseui-auth-container</code>인 div 태그를 만든다.</p>\n<p>페이지가 렌더링 될 때 mounted에서는 현재 로그인 한 사용자가 있는지 아닌지를 파악한다.  만약 로그인 한 사용자가 없을 경우에는 로그인 창을 렌더링 한다.</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1b97d09f03dff0c0204da3eda516d103/5b815/firebase-login-email2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 644px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 79.03726708074534%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"firebase-login-email2\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/1b97d09f03dff0c0204da3eda516d103/5b815/firebase-login-email2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1b97d09f03dff0c0204da3eda516d103/0783d/firebase-login-email2.png 240w,\n/static/1b97d09f03dff0c0204da3eda516d103/782f4/firebase-login-email2.png 480w,\n/static/1b97d09f03dff0c0204da3eda516d103/5b815/firebase-login-email2.png 644w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 644px) 100vw, 644px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>이메일을 입력 후 이름과 비밀번호를 입력하면 자동으로 회원가입이 된다.</p>\n<p>firebase의 authnetication에 접속하면 가입한 사람을 볼 수 있다.</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a5a1d2b7ef0961054bb843cd38035084/de00b/firebase-authenticaion2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 960px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 40.94202898550725%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"firebase-authenticaion2\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/a5a1d2b7ef0961054bb843cd38035084/f570d/firebase-authenticaion2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a5a1d2b7ef0961054bb843cd38035084/0783d/firebase-authenticaion2.png 240w,\n/static/a5a1d2b7ef0961054bb843cd38035084/782f4/firebase-authenticaion2.png 480w,\n/static/a5a1d2b7ef0961054bb843cd38035084/f570d/firebase-authenticaion2.png 960w,\n/static/a5a1d2b7ef0961054bb843cd38035084/de00b/firebase-authenticaion2.png 1104w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<h2 id=\"google-login\"><a href=\"#google-login\" aria-label=\"google login permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>google login</h2>\n<p>구글 로그인은 페이스북 로그인에 비해 비교적 간단한 편이다. firebase에서만 구현이 가능하다.</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1e504c4b390b116decf550570e060584/823b0/firebase-google-login.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 954px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 82.49475890985325%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"firebase-google-login\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/1e504c4b390b116decf550570e060584/823b0/firebase-google-login.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1e504c4b390b116decf550570e060584/0783d/firebase-google-login.png 240w,\n/static/1e504c4b390b116decf550570e060584/782f4/firebase-google-login.png 480w,\n/static/1e504c4b390b116decf550570e060584/823b0/firebase-google-login.png 954w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 954px) 100vw, 954px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>이메일에서 했던것과 같이 로그인 방법에서 구글 로그인의 사용 설정을 열어준 후, 웹 SDK 구성의 웹 클라이언트 ID를 복사해둔다.</p>\n<p>이후 <code class=\"language-text\">Login.vue</code>의 signInOptions를 수정한다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">signInoptions<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n          firebase<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>auth<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>EmailAuthProvider<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token constant\">PROVIDER_ID</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n              provider<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> firebase<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>auth<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>GoogleAuthProvider<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token constant\">PROVIDER_ID</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n              authMethod<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"https://accounts.google.com\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n              clientId<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n                <span class=\"token string\">\"클라이언트 아이디\"</span>\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n          <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>위에서 복사해 둔 클라이언트 ID를 넣어준다.</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/34ab873dfeac0e5592f20753539c86b8/39eb8/firebase-login.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 379px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 97.36147757255938%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"firebase-login-google\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/34ab873dfeac0e5592f20753539c86b8/39eb8/firebase-login.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/34ab873dfeac0e5592f20753539c86b8/0783d/firebase-login.png 240w,\n/static/34ab873dfeac0e5592f20753539c86b8/39eb8/firebase-login.png 379w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 379px) 100vw, 379px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<h3 id=\"ref\"><a href=\"#ref\" aria-label=\"ref permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Ref</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/firebase/firebaseui-web\">firebaseui-web</a> </p>","fields":{"slug":"/firebase/using-firebaseui/","tagSlugs":["/tag/firebase/","/tag/firebaseui/","/tag/vue/","/tag/vue-js/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2019-07-17T17:19:00.169Z","description":"firebaseui를 사용해 vue에서 로그인 환경 구축하기","tags":["firebase","firebaseui","Vue","vue.js"],"title":"firebaseui로 로그인 따라하기 (이메일, 구글, 페이스북) (with Vue.js)"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/firebase/using-firebaseui/"}}}